      "hasReports": false,
      "body": [
        "她说儿子3岁多，感冒咳嗽一个多月了，到北京儿童医院西医也看了，还做了过敏源检查，也找其他中医挂300一人的中医专家也看了，可就是咳嗽反复老不好，不知是什么原理？经详细问得知，儿子平时喜吹空调吃冷饮，原来由自己带着控制得还好，很少发生感冒咳嗽，近两个月，由一亲戚来带小孩，小孩要什么都满足小孩，小孩要空调就立即给开空调。。。。。结果感冒后一拖就一个多月了，多方治疗就是不好，现在还在反复咳嗽。我问流鼻涕吗？答：流。是清鼻涕吗？是的！我说：很明显，就是在反复进行风寒感冒！我说你把专家的中药处方拿来我看看。处方拿来一看，基本就是一些清热、消炎、镇咳、化痰类药。我说，这处方方向反了，寒病用了寒药。直接解表就行，别怕小孩出汗，流流汗就好了。给直接开了付辛温解表药，嘱吃3付。次周我一去坐诊，店长立即上前来说：袁大夫，真如你说一样，一吃就见效，汗一出，就不咳了！"
      ],
      "images": [
        "img/case_16_1.png"
      ],
      "bodyEn": [
        "She said her son is just over 3 years old and has had a cold with cough for over a month. He's been seen at Beijing Children's Hospital by Western medicine doctors, had allergen tests done, and even consulted a TCM 'expert' charging 300 yuan per visit — yet the cough keeps recurring and won't go away. She couldn't understand why. Upon detailed questioning, I learned that the child often likes to have the air conditioner on and eats cold drinks. Previously, when she was the primary caregiver, she maintained good control and the child rarely had colds or coughs. In the past two months, a relative has been looking after the child and indulges his every wish — whenever the child wants the air conditioner on, it's switched on immediately... As a result, after catching a cold, it dragged on for over a month. Despite multiple treatments, it simply wouldn't resolve, and the child was still coughing on and off. I asked: 'Is his nose running?' She replied: 'Yes.' 'Is it clear nasal discharge?' 'Yes!' I said: 'It's obvious — he's having repeated wind-cold invasions!' I asked her to show me the TCM expert's prescription. When I saw it, it was basically just heat-clearing, anti-inflammatory, cough-suppressing, and phlegm-resolving herbs. I told her: 'This prescription is going in the wrong direction — a cold illness treated with cold herbs. Directly release the exterior — that's all you need. Don't be afraid of the child sweating. Let him sweat it out and he'll be fine.' I prescribed a simple acrid-warm exterior-releasing formula and instructed 3 doses. The following week when I arrived at the clinic, the store manager immediately approached me and said: 'Doctor Yuan, it's exactly as you said — it took effect right away. Once he sweat, the coughing stopped!'"
      ]
