        "Lu XX, male, 43 years old. First visit: May 3, 2011.",
        "Referred by a friend, he traveled by train from another city to seek treatment.",
        "In 2004, sudden onset of hepatitis B (at that time: liver region distension, stomach pain, elevated bilirubin).",
