        "Lü XX, female, 63 years old.",
        "2012/3/14 First visit: systemic hot flashes with sweating for 8-9 years, recurring many times daily; during episodes, vexation and agitation, unable to control herself, face fully flushed, sweat pouring like rain over the whole body (episodes occur regardless of day or night). Frequently sees phantom images before her eyes (familiar acquaintances or strangers), accompanied by tinnitus, forgetfulness, sudden panic attacks; history of heart disease (sinus arrhythmia); difficulty falling asleep, shallow sleep, unstable sleep quality. Nocturia once; fair appetite; formed bowel movement once daily. Tongue edges with tooth marks, scant thin slippery coating; pulse slippery-rapid. 6-year history of diabetes, history of hypertension, history of headaches, history of elevated uric acid.",
        "Pattern differentiation: heart, liver, and kidney yin deficiency; spleen and lung qi deficiency.",
        "Ophiopogon japonicus, Platycladus orientalis, Ziziphus spinosa, Scrophularia ningpoensis, Polygonum multiflorum, Schisandra chinensis, Bupleurum chinense, Os Draconis and Ostrea gigas, Pueraria lobata, Atractylodes macrocephala, Ziziphus jujuba, Gallus gallus endothelium corneum, Hordeum vulgare germinatum, Coptis chinensis, Glycyrrhiza uralensis.",
