        "2012/3/28 Third visit: dry mouth upon waking and sleep improved; hot flashes and sweating reduced; palpitations improved; palms and soles hot with sweating.",
        "2012/4/6 Fourth visit: sleep further improved; hot flashes and sweating continued to reduce. Sensation of abdominal distension. Adjusted prescription, added Crataegus pinnatifida to fortify the spleen and promote digestion.",
        "2012/4/13 Fifth visit: sleep further improved; duration of each hot-flash-sweating episode reduced. Palpitations essentially did not recur. Abdominal distension resolved. Patient reported: had splenomegaly since youth. Self-monitored blood glucose indices fluctuating unstably.",
        "2012/4/20 Sixth visit: same as above.",
        "2012/4/27 Seventh visit: reported history of gallstones (multiple, largest 1.3x0.9 cm), history of fatty liver, history of leg varicose veins. Hot flashes further markedly improved; tinnitus and urinary frequency still present.",
        "2012/5/4 Eighth visit: caught a cold midway; now fatigued, dry throat and hoarse voice, nasal discharge of yellow mucus.",
        "First address the external contraction: Arctium lappa, Forsythia suspensa, Houttuynia cordata, Fritillaria thunbergii, Saposhnikovia divaricata, Poria cocos, Scrophularia ningpoensis, Ziziphus spinosa, Peucedanum praeruptorum, Rabdosia rubescens, Glycyrrhiza uralensis.",
        "2012/5/11 Ninth visit: phlegm in throat, throat itch with cough; hot flashes still present 1-2 times daily (very mild compared to before).",
        "Blood pressure 130/80; blood glucose 6.8.",
        "2012/5/18 Tenth visit: sore throat with phlegm; sleep acceptable; hot flashes 1-2 times daily; sweaty palms.",
