        "Third week: bathroom frequency remained the same, but the body experienced no sense of weakness from the frequent loose stools. Instead, energy felt gradually restored; episodes of irritability decreased; facial skin color lightened; and the facial skin was slowly regenerating and smoothing out. When compared with photos taken at the first consultation, the results were direct and obvious.",
        "Currently, after over 2 months of continuous medication, facial skin has largely recovered. Broken capillaries are basically covered by newly generated skin; the skin surface is fine and smooth. The psoriatic plaques on the body have greatly improved; the bumps and plaques on the scalp have improved most dramatically. After washing my hair,",
