        "Lei XX",
        "15:25:26",
        "Yeah, at the time I thought if Chinese medicine didn't work either, the only option left would be dilation and curettage — that would have been even more trouble.",
        "Lei XX",
        "15:25:51",
        "Thank goodness.",
        "Lei XX",
        "18:16:25",
        "OK, so is it all right with the cold now?",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:16:29",
        "2017.2.15 Prescription:",
        "Huoxiang, Zisu, Huangqi, Dangshen, Cangzhu, Maidong, Jiaoshanzha, Jiaomaiya, Muxiang, Fuling, Shanyao, Shengma, Huangqin, Baishao, Shanzhuyu, Duanlonggu (pounded finely), Xianhecao, Gancao",
        "Seven doses",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:17:22",
        "How can you say it's all right? Just keep taking the medicine. She's too depleted — that's why she's prone to catching colds.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:17:54",
        "In this condition, she's still going to work?",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:18:20",
        "If you can rest, rest and recuperate as much as possible. Don't push yourself so hard.",
        "Lei XX",
        "18:18:20",
        "She's already taken one day off.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:18:32",
        "Mm.",
        "Lei XX",
        "18:19:05",
        "Yeah, too many patients. It's a private clinic. Just keep taking the medicine you prescribed — she'll be fine.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:19:43",
        "In her condition, she is already a seriously ill patient herself.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:20:06",
        "If she really collapses, she'll regret it later.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:20:19",
        "So she really needs to rest well.",
        "Lei XX",
        "18:20:32",
        "Mm, OK.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:20:54",
        "Mm, let's leave it at that then.",
        "Lei XX",
        "18:21:46",
        "I'm going to get the prescription filled now.",
        "Dr. Yuan",
        "18:21:50",
        "Mm."
