        "History of chronic bronchitis, frequent susceptibility to colds triggering coughing and asthma for many years, often accompanied by yellow nasal discharge, dry mouth, hot breath, vaginitis, poor sleep, and early waking. On a friend's recommendation, she began receiving Chinese herbal medicine from me on December 16, 2014 for constitutional regulation. Through intermittent treatment her overall physical condition steadily improved. Since starting the herbs, she had essentially not experienced any severe episodes of coughing, wheezing, or bronchitis symptoms. The occasional mild cold symptoms passed quickly.",
