        "2013.1.3 Second Visit: Effect was noticeable from the very first dose — lower abdominal pain lessened. By the third dose, the lower abdominal distending pain had markedly improved. After finishing the fourth dose, the abdominal pain and internal cold sensation were about 70% resolved. He said that in all the years since this illness began, no treatment had ever produced such obvious results. He was visibly very happy and excited on the spot.",
        "2013.1.10",
        "Third Visit: The periumbilical region no longer feels cold; he no longer needs to use a heat pad. Abdominal distention and pain are gone. Frequent flatulence; no more hyper-reactive abdominal pain upon defecation.",
