      "body": [
        "个人简介：邹某，女，27岁，已婚，山东威海人，在北京生活两年多",
        "治疗感言：之前我有痛经的问题，而且是属于疼的站不起来的那种，有朋友（之前也在袁大夫看过病）建议我看看中医，因为之前没接触过，所以就一直拖着。2012年3月底发了次烧，之前吃了退烧药很快就会好转，但那次吃完药之后没有任何反应，因为担心身体，就找袁大夫看了看。",
        "诊断：袁大夫说我肾肝虚，因为这个所以抵抗力会弱，我还没说我之前那些没当回事儿的症状，他就一一说了虚会导致的症状：抑郁（消极、心慌、多疑等）、多梦（怪异、惊险类）、磨牙、眼睛干累、痛经、妇科炎症等，我之前偶尔会出现守不住神的感觉，就像魂走了似的，而且在耳边会出现一种消极的声音，两秒钟又恢复了，恢复之后就有点精神不振，身体也没劲了，袁大夫说就是肾虚导致的，而且我还是属于那种先天性不足的，像这种体质要少吃鱼、羊、牛、鸡、鸭肉，说是发性食品。我很佩服大夫说的，因为之前吃这些东西真的吃的很多，所以很乖的喝药，虽然苦口。",
        "体会：袁大夫先给我开了三幅治退烧和感冒药，一付煎三次，如果不是亲身体会，真不知道中药治退烧和感冒如此之快，第一天烧就退了，到第三天就不流鼻涕了（第二天还用纸堵的鼻子），身体明显有劲儿、有精神了，第四天上班我就正常了，就是声音稍有点鼻音。",
        "发烧治好后，我开始按照袁大夫的治疗计划开始调理，还是一幅药煎三次，一天三次，因为中午怕在办公室喝药有味，我就早晚喝，喝完之后立马有反应，排毒期最多一天能排便7-8次，随着调理的进展，排便次数减少，磨牙明显减轻。",
        "由于我的体内有湿气，再加上夏天晚上开窗睡，晚上比较容易爱着凉，会出现恶心症状，只要喝些霍香正气液（水或胶囊）、保济口服液就可以了，很管用。袁大夫嘱咐我，如果实在想吃鱼、肉，每次吃完了喝碗绿豆汤就可以了，还让我平时多吃冬瓜（排湿）。",
        "4个月后",
        "现在是补力量的阶段，其中补药里有一味黄芪，吃了一两天，明显感觉身体里有股很强的力量，也可以说是底气，这真是我前所未有的感觉。",
        "6个月后",
        "随着调理的进展和更新药方，身体越来越好了，再也没有魂飘了的感觉，精神非常充沛，能吃能睡，而且抵抗力增强了，例假微疼，我不希望调理的一点感觉没有，没有征兆也不好，而且我之前的脸虽然很干净，但是脸色黄、发暗，现在我的脸又白又细腻，同事都说我皮肤变化很大，而且现在调理的差不多了，大夫说可以要小孩儿了，还好让袁大夫瞧了，要不以我之前的体格要孩子可遭罪了。我很庆幸看了中医，要不以后会出现更多的问题，现在“根”治好了，心里踏实很多。我写体会的目的，一是真心感谢袁大夫把我身体的问题都调理好了，让我有了新的生命力，而且他是我最信任的中医大夫；二是我希望有跟我病情相似的朋友早调理早健康，要配合医生的治疗，坚持就是胜利。2012/9/18"
      ],
      "bodyEn": [
        "Personal profile: Zou, female, 27 years old, married, from Weihai, Shandong. Has been living in Beijing for over two years.",
        "Treatment testimonial: I previously had dysmenorrhea so severe I couldn't stand up. A friend (who had also seen Dr. Yuan before) suggested I try traditional Chinese medicine. Since I had no prior experience with it, I kept putting it off. In late March 2012, I had a fever. Previously, taking antipyretics would quickly bring relief, but this time there was no response at all. Worried about my health, I went to see Dr. Yuan.",
        "Diagnosis: Dr. Yuan said I had liver and kidney deficiency, which weakened my resistance. Before I even mentioned the symptoms I hadn't taken seriously, he listed all the symptoms that deficiency could cause: depression (negativity, palpitations, paranoia, etc.), excessive dreaming (bizarre, frightening types), teeth grinding, dry and tired eyes, dysmenorrhea, gynecological inflammation, etc. I had occasionally experienced a sensation of not being able to hold onto my spirit, as if my soul had departed, accompanied by a negative inner voice for a couple of seconds before recovering. Afterward I'd feel slightly dazed and physically weak. Dr. Yuan said this was all due to kidney deficiency, and that I had a constitutionally weak foundation from birth. With this constitution, I should eat less fish, lamb, beef, chicken, and duck — he called these 'stimulating foods.' I was very impressed by the doctor's analysis, because I really had been eating a lot of those foods. So I obediently took the medicine, bitter as it was.",
        "Experience: Dr. Yuan first prescribed three doses to treat the fever and cold — one dose decocted three times. If I hadn't experienced it firsthand, I would never have known how quickly Chinese medicine can treat fever and colds. The fever subsided on the first day, and by the third day the runny nose stopped (on the second day I was still plugging my nose with tissue). My body clearly felt stronger and more energetic. By the fourth day I was back to normal at work, just with a slightly nasal voice.",
        "After the fever was cured, I began Dr. Yuan's treatment plan for constitutional regulation — still one dose decocted three times a day, taken three times daily. Afraid of the smell of the medicine in the office at noon, I took it morning and evening instead. Right after taking it, there would be an immediate reaction. During the detoxification phase, I had up to 7–8 bowel movements a day. As treatment progressed, the frequency decreased, and my teeth grinding significantly reduced.",
        "Because my body had internal dampness, plus sleeping with windows open in summer, I was prone to catching cold at night, which would cause nausea. Taking Huoxiang Zhengqi liquid (or capsules) or Baoji oral liquid was very effective. Dr. Yuan instructed that if I really wanted to eat fish or meat, I should drink a bowl of mung bean soup afterward. He also advised me to eat more winter melon regularly (to expel dampness).",
        "After 4 months",
        "Now in the strength-building phase, one of the tonic herbs is Huang Qi (Astragalus). After taking it for just a day or two, I clearly felt a strong surge of power within my body — what you could call inner confidence. This was a feeling I had truly never experienced before.",
        "After 6 months",
        "As treatment progressed with updated prescriptions, my body got better and better. The 'soul-drifting' sensation never returned. I was full of energy, eating and sleeping well, and my resistance was stronger. Menstrual pain was only mild — I wouldn't want it completely painless anyway; having no warning signs isn't good either. Though my face had always been clear, my complexion was sallow and dull. Now my face is fair, bright, and smooth. Colleagues all say my skin has changed dramatically. Now that my constitution is nearly fully regulated, the doctor says I can try for a baby. Thankfully I saw Dr. Yuan — with my previous constitution, pregnancy would have been miserable. I'm very grateful I tried Chinese medicine; otherwise more problems would have emerged later. Now that the 'root' has been treated, I feel much more at ease. My purpose in writing this testimonial is twofold: first, to sincerely thank Dr. Yuan for regulating all my health issues and giving me a new vitality — he is the TCM doctor I trust most; second, I hope friends with similar conditions will seek treatment early and recover early. Cooperate with the doctor's treatment — persistence is victory. September 18, 2012"
      ]
