      "bodyEn": [
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:11:11",
        "The formula has consistently included Guizhi, yet subjectively there are no exterior syndrome symptoms.",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:13:55",
        "Using modified Fuzi Lizhong Decoction combined with Taoren Siwu Decoction and Sanren Decoction: the first dose showed obvious effect — hands and feet warmed back up, even felt the numbness and distention in hands and feet rapidly improved, but thereafter the effect was no longer significant.",
        "Unsure why. Suspect it might be related to eating sweet potatoes in the following days. Let's discuss.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 2011-3-22 17:15:15",
        "Haha, Fuzi, please describe all her pulse signs and symptoms in detail.",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:19:56",
        "Diabetes: Western diagnosis — high blood sugar, urine sugar normal. Controlled within normal range on oral hypoglycemic drugs and insulin injections.",
        "Chief complaint symptoms: Numbness and distention in hands and feet; more pronounced in right hand's index, middle, ring, and little fingers, and left foot's big toe and second toe. After treatment, right hand index and middle finger significantly improved; others still numb and distended. Mild in the morning, severe in the evening.",
        "Pulse: thready, thin, weak, and forceless; cannot withstand pressure. Left cun position floating and tight.",
        "Tongue: pale with thin white coating (originally white thick greasy coating).",
        "No thirst or polyuria symptoms.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:21:53",
        "These kinds of conditions probably don't show dramatic effects that quickly, right...",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:22:08",
        "Oh yes — fingertips are red and sweaty.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:22:13",
        "Phlegm-dampness should be quite severe, I think...",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:22:30",
        "How can you tell that phlegm-dampness is severe?",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:22:57",
        "I misread it... sorry... (originally white thick greasy coating)",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:22:58",
        "No frequent phlegm or cough symptoms observed; only occasional in the morning.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:24:06",
        "I don't really understand... haha...",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:24:42",
        "No worries — those who do understand, please analyze!",
        "Those who don't understand can also guess.",
        "Learning is exactly this kind of process.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:25:29",
        "Yes indeed... I've only read less than one third of the Shanghan Lun... haha...",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:25:50",
        "Take a look at famous doctors' case records for treating this kind of condition...",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:26:15",
        "The Fire Spirit school uses Zhenwu Decoction and Danggui Sini Decoction.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:27:07",
        "Sigh... Fire Spirit school cases are few, unfortunately...",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:27:16",
        "Take a look at classical-formula school doctors' case records...",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:33:17",
        "So disappointing — every time nobody speaks up.",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:37:10",
        "No need to be disappointed...",
        "Xinggu Dadao (312667596) 2011-3-22 17:37:15",
        "Others just don't understand either... can't be helped...",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:44:33",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:33:17",
        "So disappointing — every time nobody speaks up — what's the problem?",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:44:49",
        "Tell me about it.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 17:47:18",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 17:19:56",
        "Diabetes: Western diagnosis — high blood sugar, urine sugar normal. Controlled within normal range on oral hypoglycemic drugs and insulin injections.",
        "Chief complaint symptoms: Numbness and distention in hands and feet; more pronounced in right hand's index, middle, ring, and little fingers, and left foot's big toe and second toe. After treatment, right hand index and middle finger significantly improved; others still numb and distended. Mild in the morning, severe in the evening.",
        "Pulse: thready, thin, weak, and forceless; cannot withstand pressure. Left cun position floating and tight.",
        "Tongue: pale with thin white coating (originally white thick greasy coating).",
        "No thirst or polyuria symptoms.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:50:52",
        "Pulse thready, thin, weak, and forceless; cannot withstand pressure — indicates severe qi and blood deficiency, liver and kidney insufficiency.",
        "Left cun floating and tight — possibly slight contraction of wind-cold.",
        "Tongue pale with thin white coating (originally white thick greasy coating) — possibly slight contraction of wind-cold.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:52:47",
        "Fuzi (673303882) 2011-3-22 17:22:08",
        "Oh yes — fingertips red and sweaty — indicates heart fire; may be related to accumulated heat from using Fuzi.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 17:54:50",
        "Haha, so what method should be used to resolve it?",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:54:54",
        "No thirst — though there is heart fire, if there is exterior cold, thirst may not necessarily be present.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 17:55:15",
        "The key is whether it's deficiency or excess.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 17:55:26",
        "I feel it's more deficiency.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:55:44",
        "Mixed deficiency and excess, but predominantly deficiency.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:56:36",
        "Fuzi: In yang deficiency patterns, short-term use is acceptable; it should not be used long-term, or should be used intermittently.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:57:54",
        "Fuzi is similar to Western hormonal drugs — short-term use produces immediate results, but long-term use damages genuine yin.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 17:59:32",
        "For long-term kidney yang support, one may use Buguzhi, Tusizi, Gouqizi, and the like.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 18:00:05",
        "Mm, I feel we should first supplement deficiency; releasing the exterior for wind-cold should come after.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:00:41",
        "In supporting yang, you can add wind-dispersing and exterior-releasing herbs.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:00:52",
        "To address immediate needs.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 18:01:01",
        "Mm, diabetes is essentially liver, kidney, and spleen yin deficiency.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:01:26",
        "Both yin and yang are deficient.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:02:04",
        "It's just that some lean more toward yang deficiency, some lean more toward yin deficiency — varies by individual.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 18:02:12",
        "Both yin and yang deficient is precisely true-yuan depletion.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:02:18",
        "Yes.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:02:46",
        "Therefore, supplementing kidney yin and yang is indispensable.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:03:39",
        "This is just my personal view — throwing out a brick to attract jade.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 18:03:53",
        "Mm, the Neijing says yang wanes as yin grows, yin wanes as yang grows.",
        "Weichen (974739512) 18:04:21",
        "So, is there any more specific approach?",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:04:52",
        "In diabetes, clinical presentations often show signs of liver, spleen, and kidney multi-organ deficiency.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:05:24",
        "Therefore, treatment for this condition should regulate all three organs simultaneously.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:05:59",
        "Wood, earth, water — regulate their balance.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:06:35",
        "Once the physiological functions of these three organs improve, the condition will also improve and can be cured.",
        "Lebu (357522452) 18:07:00",
        "There is no single fixed formula that would work — the prescription must be flexibly adjusted."
      ]
