        "If you had the ability to evaluate my prescription, you wouldn't need to come to me or any other doctor for treatment.",
        "2011-1-13 10:27:37 Le Bu",
        "Just take the medicine first. I understand your concern.",
        "2011-1-13 10:29:58 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Sir, you're a good person. Thank you for understanding!",
        "2011-1-13 10:31:29 Le Bu",
        "There are many patients with the same mindset as you, especially those who have learned some TCM knowledge — they all, like you, use their own TCM knowledge to evaluate the doctor's medication.",
        "2011-1-13 10:32:51 Le Bu",
        "In TCM, the good and the bad are intermingled. In the current era, there aren't many who can truly use Chinese herbs well.",
        "2011-1-13 10:34:31 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Because I've taken quite a lot of Chinese herbs without full recovery, I'm somewhat worried. Sir, as the saying goes, a doctor has a parental heart — please forgive me!",
        "2011-1-13 10:34:42 Le Bu",
        "I consider everyone who encounters me to be connected by fate. I always give very serious diagnosis and treatment, and I truly treasure this illness-based affinity.",
        "2011-1-13 10:36:04 Le Bu",
        "So you don't need to worry that I'll be displeased. Any patient I take on, I will treat seriously until they are cured.",
        "2011-1-13 10:37:13 Le Bu",
        "You just need to take your medicine conscientiously. Within 1-2 weeks, there will basically be obvious results.",
        "2011-1-13 10:37:44 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "I'll do as you say, sir.",
        "2011-1-13 10:38:14 Le Bu",
        "Good.",
        "2011-1-13 10:40:23 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Thank you, sir!",
        "2011-1-13 10:46:49 Le Bu",
        "2011-1-11 16:12:06 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
