        "2011-1-25 19:51:35 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Since the day before yesterday, my teeth have started hurting. Any good solutions?",
        "(This message was sent by your friend via Mobile QQ. To try Mobile QQ, please visit: http://mobile.qq.com/c )",
        "2011-1-25 20:02:23 Le Bu",
        "Use: 15g of raw Da Huang steeped in freshly boiled water, like making tea. Then each time you take your medicine, add 30-50ml of the Da Huang infusion. Afterward, bowel movement frequency will increase. Aim for 3-4 bowel movements per day as the standard. If bowel movements become too frequent, reduce the Da Huang infusion; if insufficient, increase it. After a few days of bowel evacuation, the heat will exit through the stool and the tooth pain will resolve. Once the tooth pain is gone, stop using the Da Huang infusion.",
        "2011-1-25 20:04:25 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
