        "Just persist with the medicine.",
        "2011-1-27 09:15:38 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Sir, I previously took this formula: Dang Gui 10g, Bai Shao 15g, Chai Hu 15g, Bai Zhu 10g, Dan Pi 20g, Zhi Zi 20g, Suan Zao Ren 0g, Fu Shen 20g, Mu Xiang 10g, Long Chi 30g, Huang Lian 6g, Da Zao 20g, Yuan Zhi 8g, Mai Dong 15g, Mu Li 30g, Chang Pu 6g, Chi Xiao Dou 20g, Gan Cao 5g. I took it for about ten-plus doses. Does that affect things? Also, what exactly does this formula treat?",
        "2011-1-27 10:56:31 Le Bu",
        "Don't worry about the past. Just take the medicine as instructed now. Record your current symptoms carefully, and after completing one course of the prescribed formula as required, give your feedback. I'll then prescribe according to the condition. I won't comment on other people's prescriptions.",
        "2011-1-27 11:16:31 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
