        "2011-1-27 11:18:33 Le Bu",
        "Until your illness is completely cured.",
        "2011-1-27 11:22:53 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "OK.",
        "2011-1-27 12:57:24 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "Sir, I'm sending you the follow-up consultation form.",
        "2011-1-27 12:58:29 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "1. Under natural diffuse light: tongue body pale red, no scalloped edges, tongue coating pale white. 2. Pulse rate 85 beats per minute. 3. Tongue coating is slightly paler than during the previous diagnosis. 4. During this period of taking medicine, no dry or bitter mouth, drinking water the same as usual. 5. During these days of taking medicine, no bitter mouth upon waking in the morning, no other abnormal tastes. 6. During this period of taking medicine, stools somewhat loose, black in color, basically formed, once daily. Urine pale in color. 7. Sleep has now improved — easier to fall asleep, easier to fall back asleep after waking in the middle of the night. Still basically waking two or three times. Upon waking in the morning, more energetic than before. 8. Appetite has improved compared to before — about two and a half bowls of rice per meal. 9. Now I feel clearly improved compared to before taking the medicine: vision is clearer, palpitations and rapid heartbeat are less frequent, hands and feet are stronger, less fatigue from physical work. The lumbar soreness situation",
        "2011-1-27 13:00:12 Ordinary Tow Truck Guy",
        "The lumbar soreness has improved. 10. I've noticed the following conditions that I hope can be further improved: a feeling of head distension, occasional palpitations and rapid heartbeat still appear, sometimes I feel totally listless with no fighting spirit and no interest in anything. Lumbar soreness still present but lighter than before taking the medicine. After four or five doses, the gums became slightly swollen and painful. During bowel movements and when passing gas, there's a burning sensation at the anus. 11. Currently no excessive sweating — the tendency to sweat easily has changed. 12. Upon getting up in the morning, legs and feet are somewhat sore and weak. The gas passed is very foul-smelling.",
        "2011-1-27 15:36:29 Le Bu",
        "Dang Shen, Huang Qi, Mai Dong, Bai He, Fu Ling, Shan Yu Rou, Wu Wei, Mu Xiang, Ci Shi, raw Long Gu and Mu Li, Shu Di, Dan Shen, Gou Qi, Mai Ya, Sang Ji Sheng, Dang Gui, Shan Yao, Huai Niu Xi, Gan Cao.",
