        "Infertility, irregular menstruation (delayed cycle), flooding and spotting (beng lou), breast hyperplasia with small cysts (endocrine tests: high prolactin, low progesterone), pelvic inflammatory disease, salpingitis, severe cervical erosion, cervical spondylosis, chronic pharyngitis, mixed hemorrhoids. Over the years: Western antibiotics, hormones; Chinese herbal medicine (hundreds of doses of blood-activating stasis-resolving, liver-soothing kidney-tonifying, and spleen-fortifying formulas); Chinese patent medicines (Xiao Yao Wan, Gui Pi Wan, Gong Xue Ning, Fu Yan Kang; external gynecological washes, Dakening suppositories, povidone-iodine suppositories, etc.)",
        "13. For women: Menstrual condition? Is timing normal each month? Is color normal? Amount—heavy or scanty daily flow? How many days until clean? Any purple-black blood clots?",
