        "XXX Apr 6, 2010 20:42:43",
        "Started taking medicine at noon on Apr 5; dizziness, body heaviness; no obvious sensation after taking it. The taste is quite good, slightly sweet. It seems foul flatulence is slightly more frequent; very comfortable after passing gas. Stools slightly dry; poor sleep.",
        "Apr 7: Non-stop sneezing upon waking in the morning; rhinitis has worsened recently—hurriedly put on an extra cotton coat. Bowel movements twice today; the second time unformed, loose stools, dark yellow-green. Yellow urine; a bout of genital itching; slight tofu-residue-like leukorrhea. Took medicine around 9pm last night; woke up at midnight with a full bladder. The last 2 days' urine still seems turbid, with unusual odor, which may also be from the leukorrhea. Pants have a strong smell after just one day—not sure if it's still a urinary tract infection. Today decocting the second dose of medicine.",
